data.description: Welcome to this stunning home located in SW Hartselle, AL! This spacious residence offers 6 bedrooms and 3 and a half bathrooms. It has plenty of room for entertaining guests and a separate living space in the basement with its own entrance. The well-appointed kitchen has ample cabinetry and the dining area provides lovely space for enjoying meals with family and friends. The living room boasts a soaring ceiling and windows with plenty of natural light. The primary bedroom has two walk-in closets and a relaxing glamour bathroom. This home has lots of curb appeal showcasing the 1.2 acres of land and beautiful back deck and a inviting front porch. The possibilities are endless!
